# Reflection on Mock Interview Video Experience (STAR Method)

## Situation

As part of the work readiness portfolio, I participated in a mock interview video exercise designed to simulate a real job interview environment.

## Task

My responsibility was to answer interview questions professionally while demonstrating confidence, communication skills, and proper interview etiquette. I also needed to reflect on my performance using the STAR method.

## Action

To prepare, I practiced common interview questions and focused on improving my communication skills. During the interview, I maintained professionalism, attempted to speak clearly, and structured my responses carefully. After reviewing the video, I reflected on my body language, confidence, and speaking pace.

## Result

The mock interview experience helped me identify both strengths and areas for improvement. I learned the importance of preparation, confidence, and structured communication during interviews. The activity also increased my confidence and gave me valuable experience for future employment opportunities.

